---
title: Simple Soy and Honey Glazed Prawns with Garlicky Beans and Bulgur Wheat
description: We love good Simply Soy and Honey Glazed Prawns and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/simple-soy-and-honey-glazed-prawns-358bf141-32d598d6.jpg
